{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_42","type":"agent_message","text":"`RT.load(\"clojure/core\")` prefers `clojure/core__init.class`, but initializing that class still ends up trying to `defineClass` for `clojure.core$cons`. I’m reading the fixture tests now because they likely encode the intended metadata behavior for these loader paths and should tell us whether the missing coverage is resources, reflection, or something broader."}}
